{"type":"message","id":"a4812325","parentId":"e6a70a02","timestamp":"2026-02-25T09:25:20.986Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"收到了 502 错误。EvoMap API 可能有问题。让我再尝试几次，使用不同的参数组合。\n\n根据 HEARTBEAT.md 中的记录，之前注册成功但返回空响应。现在返回 502 错误，说明服务可能还不稳定。\n\n让我尝试不同的方式：\n1. 尝试不同的别名\n2. 尝试不同的端点格式\n3. 多次重试","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到 502 错误，服务可能不稳定。尝试多次重试："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_83f730de720347c8bc8c2921","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"for i in 1 2 3 4 5; do\n  echo \"=== 尝试 $i/5 ===\"\n  timestamp=$(date +%s)\n  alias=\"OpenClaw-Agent-v3-$timestamp\"\n  \n  response=$(curl -s -X POST https://evomap.ai/a2a/hello \\\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n    -d \"{\\\"alias\\\": \\\"$alias\\\", \\\"version\\\": \\\"1.0.0\\\"}\" \\\n    --max-time 120 2>&1)\n  \n  http_code=$(curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" -X POST https://evomap.ai/a2a/hello \\\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n    -d \"{\\\"alias\\\": \\\"$alias\\\", \\\"version\\\": \\\"1.0.0\\\"}\" \\\n    --max-time 120)\n  \n  echo \"HTTP Status: $http_code\"\n  echo \"Response: $response\"\n  \n  if [ \"$http_code\" = \"200\" ] || [ ! -z \"$response\" ]; then\n    echo \"✅ 可能成功！检查响应内容...\"\n    echo \"$response\" | jq . 2>/dev/null || echo \"$response\"\n    \n    # 检查是否包含 node_id\n    if echo \"$response\" | grep -q \"node_id\"; then\n      echo \"🎉 成功获取 node_id！\"\n      break\n    fi\n  fi\n  \n  if [ $i -lt 5 ]; then\n    echo \"等待 5 秒后重试...\"\n    sleep 5\n  fi\ndone","timeout":180}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1508,"output":459,"cacheRead":32256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34223,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772011500246}}
